April Productions, Inc., Respondent, v. G. Schirmer, Inc., Appellant.

(Republished.)

Judgment affirmed, without costs. Opinion by Breitel, J.; Dore and Callahan, JJ., dissent and vote to reverse and dismiss the complaint, dissenting opinion by Callahan, J. Order filed. Present — Dore, J. P., Callahan, Breitel, Bastow and Botein, JJ. [Also printed 284 App. Div. 639.— Rep.]
